<p>143. <b>The following recommendations will be examined by Maldives, which will 
</b></p>
<p><b>provide responses in due time, but no later than at the thirtieth session of the Human 
</b></p>
<p><b>Rights Council, to be held from 14 September to 2 October 2015: 
</b></p>
