</b></p>
<p><b>which it is not yet a party, among them the International Convention on the 
</b></p>
<p><b>Protection of the Rights of All Migrant Workers and Members of Their 
</b></p>
<p><b>Families (Nicaragua); </b></p>


<p>143.3 <b>Consider the possibility of ratifying the International Convention on 
</b></p>
<p><b>the Protection of the Rights of All Migrant Workers and Members of Their 
</b></p>
<p><b>Families (Egypt); 
</b></p>
